					"When the time comes, I'd like to be the kind of grown-up who can support her. Even if she is older than me.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"到时候，我希望自己能成为一位可以支持她的大人——虽然她的年纪比我大。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
